About Me

Introduction

Hi, I’m Richard K, a passionate data professional with five years of experience in the industry. My career is rooted in transforming complex data into actionable insights, helping organizations optimize their operations, drive growth, and make data-driven decisions.

I specialize in areas such as data analysis, machine learning, deep learning, risk management and predictive modeling, leveraging these skills to solve real-world problems in sectors like telecommunications, finance, and security.

Outside of work, I enjoy mentoring upcoming data professionals and contributing to the global conversation on data science through presentations and publications. I’m also passionate about continuing education, particularly in artificial intelligence and machine learning.

Professional Journey

Customer Churn Prediction

Developed a customer churn prediction model for an ISP in Kenya, reducing churn rates by 10%. This allowed the organization to proactively retain customers by identifying at-risk individuals and tailoring retention strategies.

Data Warehouse Implementation

Led a team in designing and implementing a data warehouse for a regulatory body. This project streamlined data accessibility and enhanced reporting efficiency, enabling better decision-making and faster business insights.

AI-Driven Decision Making

Presented research on AI-driven decision-making at international conferences, focusing on integrating AI and machine learning into strategic operations to make more informed decisions and maintain a competitive edge.

Mentorship and Collaboration

Passionate about mentoring and collaborating with professionals across various sectors to foster a data-driven culture. Believe in the power of cross-functional teamwork to align insights with business goals.

Education & Certifications

  • Master of Science in Data Science - University of XYZ
  • Bachelor of Science in Computer Science - University of ABC
  • Certified Data Professional (CDP)
  • Certified Machine Learning Specialist (CMLS)
